I saw this movie in the cinema in Thailand and decided I would buy the DVD when it was out. But unlike the movie version the DVD don't have English subtitles. As my Thai isn't that good I will not buy it but if you are fluent you will laugh your head off.
Why the DVD doesn't have English subtitles is a mystery to me as that would cater for a much larger audience.
